# Copy to each repo as .github/CODEOWNERS (or repo root).
# The branch ruleset's require_code_owner_review means a matching owner must
# approve before merge. Without this file, no path has an owner and that
# requirement can't be satisfied.
#
# Replace with real teams. Order matters — last match wins.

*                       @YOUR-ORG/engineering

# Lock down CI/CD and security config to a smaller group:
/.github/                @YOUR-ORG/platform
/.github/workflows/      @YOUR-ORG/platform
CODEOWNERS               @YOUR-ORG/platform
/Makefile                @YOUR-ORG/platform
